'From Squeak2.8alpha of 4 February 2000 [latest update: #1873] on 26 February 2000 at 7:12:03 pm'!"Change Set:		08ColorPrintOn-dnsDate:			6 February 2000Author:			David N SmithPrint named colors with names instead of (Color r: 0.833 g: 0.588 b: 0.524)"!!Color methodsFor: 'printing' stamp: 'dns 2/6/2000 16:14'!printOn: aStream	| name |	(name _ self name) ifNotNil:		[^ aStream			nextPutAll: self class name;			space;			nextPutAll: name].	self storeOn: aStream.! !